# ERROR TIPS
### Errors when using burner entities without fuel
- Ensure that the burner entities have a sufficient fuel supply before attempting to use them.
### Errors when using entities without ingredients
- Ensure that the entities have the necessary ingredients before attempting to use them.
### Errors when using steam engines without connection
- Ensure that the steam engines are properly connected to the electricity network before attempting to use them.
### Errors when using pipe groups without fluid
- Ensure that the pipe groups have a sufficient fluid supply before attempting to use them.
### Errors when using electricity groups without being plugged into the electric network
- Ensure that the electricity groups are properly plugged into the electric network before attempting to use them.
### Errors when using belt groups without items
- Ensure that the belt groups have items to transport before attempting to use them.
